# NEXUS Project Overview
This is a full-stack personal AI command center called NEXUS.

## Architecture
- Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite, running on port 5173
- Backend: Node.js + Express + TypeScript, running on port 3001  
- AI: Ollama running locally on port 11434 (model: llama3 or mistral)
- State: Zustand
- Drag & Drop: @dnd-kit/core
- Styling: Tailwind CSS only — never write raw CSS or inline styles

## Key Constraints
- The app MUST be non-scrollable. html, body, and #root must have overflow:hidden and height:100%
- Widget cards are absolutely positioned over a grid using getBoundingClientRect()
- Never use localStorage or sessionStorage
- All API keys live in .env — never hardcode credentials
- The backend is the ONLY place that calls Ollama — never call it from the frontend

## File Structure Reference
- Frontend components: frontend/src/components/
- Widget components: frontend/src/components/widgets/
- Custom hooks: frontend/src/hooks/
- Zustand store: frontend/src/store/useStore.ts
- Backend routes: backend/src/routes/
- Backend services: backend/src/services/
- MCP server: backend/src/mcp/

## Current Stack Versions
- React: 18
- Node: 20
- TypeScript: 5
- Vite: 5
- Tailwind: 3
